This project focuses on analyzing real-world sales data from Zepto, a quick-commerce platform. The objective was to perform end-to-end data analysis â€” from raw data cleaning to generating meaningful business insights using Python.

The dataset contains 200,000+ transactional records along with product catalog information. The project demonstrates practical implementation of data preprocessing, exploratory data analysis (EDA), aggregation, and visualization techniques.

